text: "Pati Pato" is a song recorded by Filipino rappers Shanti Dope and Gloc-9, and Parokya ni Edgar lead vocalist Chito Miranda. It was written by Sean Patrick Ramos, Alfonso Miranda, Jr., Aristotle Pollisco and Lester Vaño, and produced by Vaño credited as Klumcee. The song was released on August 29, 2019 under Universal Records. ==Track Listing== ==References== Category:2019 songs Category:Shanti Dope songs Category:Songs written by Gloc-9
